f=\"https://lih.kg/1202730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1202730</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dca966f10a9173540f51555d756f8b9f3eb7c05d","tid":1202544,"uid":119821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f52cefed948a4a886d6cb075de86d83f1f776972","tid":1202544,"uid":23590,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:17:30.000Z","msg":"我唔希望巴打你咁做 但我尊重你既決定<br />\n<br />\n如果有新轉機或者其他諗法 希望你會停止 <br />\n<br />\n加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:19:19.000Z","msg":"我唔知會有咩新轉機，但無論如何我會同大家一齊向林鄭死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8129452099a15c4cb6b30c0dd91a7b08d1cc7e5a","tid":1202544,"uid":119821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f48aefc76124db73f63e428c1328a9da0942637","tid":1202544,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e297dce2310d019a4f0f9f2d9712b699eb12140","tid":1202544,"uid":119821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5846db084506c059257eac52a74ade72a050d579","tid":1202544,"uid":37713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:11:36.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\nrespect"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:16:02.000Z","msg":"感謝 respect"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:18:16.000Z","msg":"雖然尊重你意願但我都唔希望見到有同伴犧牲<br />\n為咗咁既政府真係不太值<br />\n<br />\n最少搵個救護睇住你可以嗎？<br />\n無救護朋友 幫你推推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:19:41.000Z","msg":"謝謝你"},{"pid":"c63801f10ca0bc66bebf258dc4f735b545da1af3","tid":1202544,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:20:06.000Z","msg":"Respect bro"},{"pid":"21ed29020d795fe40e9f90acfc6d91f9f7402a3a","tid":1202544,"uid":171082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"岩！ 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eeecbb9d60dc1958a0109d73d1c70fb3bb65ddd","tid":1202544,"uid":119821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af74aca9dd334fcec39f6efb6779cb66be20239a","tid":1202544,"uid":119055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:18:25.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n但唔值為呢個仆街政權而死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:20:51.000Z","msg":"當我見大家眾志成城咁奮鬥，我唔再怕了"},{"pid":"b6e138bcce2e1c056101cec1407626e5e69d1b1c","tid":1202544,"uid":33623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:21:09.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"b6e1646063847a9d12638f51610c93006b3f1323","tid":1202544,"uid":119821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21ed29020d795fe40e9f90acfc6d91f9f7402a3a","tid":1202544,"uid":171082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"岩！ 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:22:07.000Z","msg":"大家加油"},{"pid":"9253e6e8dda645297ab2ed7d8bdfd44d3fa91ef7","tid":1202544,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:22:35.000Z","msg":"雖然自古以來 成功既革命有所犧牲係少不免 <br />\n有時我都會諗 如果真係唔好彩 雨傘果時如果犧牲左個示威者 <br />\n個結果會唔會有改變？<br />\n但我答你 係現今既香港唔會<br />\n政府回應只會係：對個表事件對示遺憾 <br />\n佢地做官既 良心不嬲有個價 做到上頭order就算 話知你死？ <br />\n所以樓主唔好做傻事 <br />\n香港呢個家係要救 但係呢個政府唔值得你為佢去死<br />\n你有呢個心 已經係出左一分力"},{"pid":"8e785e31d616b5a7bf2176b2b86a9c19ee4ad014","tid":1202544,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:23:22.000Z","msg":"唔好絕食，唔值<br />\n<br />\n共產黨理得你死"}]}